h3 Labeled avatars

p.-text
  | Avatars can be accompanied by a label. Include the avatar and the label in a div with a <code>a-avatarGroup</code>
  | class. Labeled avatars still support type, size and color variations.
.example.-mb3
  .-p3.a-grid
    each color in colors
      .-mb1.a-col.-w3
        .a-avatarGroup
          div(class=`a-avatar -${color}`) L
          = `Label ${color}`
  :code(lang="html")
    <div class="a-avatarGroup">
      <div class="a-avatar">L</div>Label text
    </div>

